Four died and 18 injured in a collision between a truck and a taxi on the N1 close to the Brandfort offramp about 20/30km from Bloemfontein direction Johannesburg on Saturday.On arrival paramedics found patients scattered across the scene. Sadly two people found in the taxi and two who were believed to have been ejected had sadly succumbed to their injuries.One person sustained critical injuries and all others sustained injuries ranging from minor to moderate.All patient were treated and transported to various hospitals.The exact cause of the incident is unknown.-TNA Reporter 